data.title: WONDER-FULL: The Magic Behind Paperswan's Photoshoot
data.meta_description: Paperswan Bride captures the essence of an elegant outdoor wedding!
data.text:
Back in November, Paperswan Bride took us to the beautiful Jacks Point in Queenstown to capture the essence of what an elegant outdoor wedding looks like. Featuring Oui The Label's Marigold and Elevate, photographer Kate encapsulated this enchantingly organised shoot!

The additional details of what a bride-to-be’s wedding could incorporate are what made this shoot oh-so-touching to us.

Elevate’s dramatic puff sleeves and Marigold’s structured, strapless bodice are contemporary wedding gowns made for the modern bride! Head over to a Paperswan Bride’s boutique, to explore more of Oui The Label's bridal gown styles.
